snippet.title: 《Soul of Eden》Global Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Hello Contestants!
Ignite the war: https://app.adjust.com/92xvmkq

The war between 4 factions is about to ignite 🔥🔥
Winning is our only goal. Everyone, get ready to battle!

🔸Know more: https://soulofeden.com/
🔸If you encounter any problems in the game, you're welcome to send an email to our customer service: service@rayark.com
